          "Married love is faithful and fruitful, signifying God's own faithfulness to his covenant (CCC 2360-2367).",
          'Persons with homosexual inclinations must be accepted with respect, compassion, and sensitivity, and are called, like all, to chastity and holiness (CCC 2358-2359).'
